{"tid":1521921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有重大進步winter on fire 終於嚟咗香港","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:52:24.000Z","uid":255646,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"40ecbbeaa375bb1676b4e71d7ee033eac4f3de79","tid":1521921,"uid":255646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"如圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先更加有爆炸聲<br />\n黑煙瀰漫<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6GsqETP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6GsqETP.png&h=d5bad558&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05qoryT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05qoryT.jpg&h=e72ddc22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6QS4kR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6QS4kR.png&h=de947bed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c36e2fcd70a4bbb42ff31988c95fd86202cb866a","tid":1521921,"uid":160247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"超興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d174d0ebefd94c82ea11cdf01a7e5b23e7f161d","tid":1521921,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. hot sodium carbonate solution<br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行"},{"pid":"e2638b35ebd7b2c4bc9aae98b99d9e48de346b42","tid":1521921,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"Summer on fire"},{"pid":"6bbb40a53d9d2897539c7fadfb827305a1f6187c","tid":1521921,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5596bd52e155385c5ce3bcdec161b280501297","tid":1521921,"uid":314979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TwAr8OW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTwAr8OW.gif&h=ed28efa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bedca42f7e0dc2562120a28f0108af09f7e8b5ec","tid":1521921,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong on Fire"},{"pid":"de4ba0ac46f5810c4fe7b8a35cffc641de482f66","tid":1521921,"uid":221237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"summer on fire"},{"pid":"511b1d81f07cf9ddec0d4b6cbdfb649bb9eae23c","tid":1521921,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"Summer on fire"},{"pid":"512b4a4fa15d30d900796c3ad92385a1baca1db2","tid":1521921,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割.Jpg"},{"pid":"a41f01db6ab0e198fcb81029edd3f1c6d7018490","tid":1521921,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"感謝所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60e86c37541fcaa84582df0d77d373090ea110e","tid":1521921,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:50.000Z","msg":"Summer on fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647937f4154da0892f0dac641549b108c10cc30b","tid":1521921,"uid":8171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/fe/83/68/fe83684d972e038f577242a311f36549.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Fo